{
  "id": "adv_main_02_03_05",
  "title": "東京編1章15話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_corridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――合宿最終日の朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Final morning of the bootcamp",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.03333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "今日で合宿もおしまいですね\nなんだか名残惜しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So the bootcamp ends today‚ eh?\nI feel a little reluctant to leave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。合宿中に新曲が出来たら良かったんだけど\n……続きは東京に戻ってからだ。ところで、みんなは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Same here. I was hoping they would finish the song during the camp‚\nbut they’ll keep working on it back in Tokyo. By the way‚ where are they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……\n一人だけどうしても目を覚まさない子がいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ummm…\nThere’s still one girl that just won’t wake up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.333333333332,
          "startTime": 23.133333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……{user}さん……\nおはようございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*yawn* Oh. {user}-san…\nGood… morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.10000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、さくら\nそれにみんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning‚ Sakura.\nGood morning‚ girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.06666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good… morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.43333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……眠い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sleepy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.83333330949149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな眠そうだな。……ん？\nじゃあ、まだまだ寝てるのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You all look exhausted. Huh?\nSo‚ that means the one still in bed is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.67687068780266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 43.61020402113597
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 43.87687068780265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "……すう……すう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahhh… Phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.71020402113598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんは低血圧なんです\nここまで寝起きが悪いのは初めてですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan has low blood pressure.\nAlthough I’ve never seen her having this much trouble waking up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.30675741036736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん！　起きて！　朝だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan! Wake up! It’s morning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2400907437007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "起きる気配……\nゼロ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Signs of waking…\n…zero percent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.017369548479735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "困りましたね\n午前中には寮を出ないといけないのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that’s a problem.\nWe’re supposed to be out of the dorm before noon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.75070288181306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "私に任せて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve got this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.28403621514639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、雫ちゃん\nその油性マジック、どうする気？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Shizuku-chan‚\nwhat’re you doing with that permanent marker?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.88403619130452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "……寝ている子は\n顔にいたずら書きされるのが……お約束",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When someone is asleep…\nwriting on their face is the standard move.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.71736952463786,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5.6843418860808015e-11,
          "startTime": 75.38403619130457
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "待て待て！　そういういたずらはやめて\nそのマジックを渡しなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute! Don’t do pranks like that.\nHand over the permanent marker!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.96736965668507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "む……私の手を掴まないで……\n……えいっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Humph. Don’t grab my hand…\nYah!…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.56736965668509,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1099.2970099815834,
          "startTime": 89.66666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Agh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.66736965668508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……騒がしいわね……\nせっかく気持ち良く寝ていたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mrrrg… so noisy…\nAnd here I was having such a good sleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6007029900184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 97.8007029900184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……え？\n誰かが私の体に覆い被さって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?\nSomebody’s on top of me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.03403632335171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "や、やあ……おはよう、怜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey… Good morning‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.03403632335171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.98403637103543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.21736970436876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあああああっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeeeeeeeeeek!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.51736970436876,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_slap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 109.51736970436876
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私は悪くありませんから！\n女子の寝込みを襲うからです！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I am not the one at fault!\nServes you right for go over a sleeping girl!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.01736970436885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "だから誤解だって……\n叩かれた頬がまだヒリヒリするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a misunderstanding…\nMy cheek still stings from the slap.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8507030377021,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3799.9999999999973,
          "startTime": 124.6507030377021
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4849.296962297899,
          "startTime": 125.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ちょっといいですか？\n出発する前にこれを見てほしいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}-san‚ got a minute?\nBefore we leave‚ there’s something I’d like to show you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.333333333331,
          "startTime": 136.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
